      content:
          'Prophet Yusuf (Joseph), peace be upon him, is the son of Prophet Yaqub (Jacob) and the great-grandson of Prophet Ibrahim (Abraham). Allah calls his story "the most beautiful of stories" in the Quran. It is a timeless account of patience, purity, and divine elevation through every human trial.',
